# Marcy Tran

This file is a template. Copy it to `FirstName_LastName.md` (e.g. `Marcy_Tran.md`), replace the content with details about a real person, and delete this `.example` version. Claude reads `People/` files when you mention a name that matches; a populated People file is how Claude remembers context across sessions instead of asking you to re-explain every call.

The example below is for an insurance advisor's group benefits client. Replace with your own.

